<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٢١٥- سَلَاّم، مَولَى نبيط، الكاهلي.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَمِعَ عليا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">رَوَى عَنه:</span> جَعفر بْن سَعد.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢٢١٦- سَلَاّم بْن عَمرو.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>رَوَى عَنه أَبو بِشر،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> رجل من قومه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>